<span>1. </span>In the name of God, the Gracious, the Merciful.</p>
<p>
<span>2. </span>Praise be to God, Lord of the Worlds.</p>
<p>
<span>3. </span>The Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.</p>
<p>
<span>4. </span>Master of the Day of Judgment.</p>
<p>
<span>5. </span>It is You we worship, and upon You we call for help.</p>
<p>
<span>6. </span>Guide us to the straight path.</p>
<p>
<span>7. </span>The path of those You have blessed, not of those against whom there is anger, nor of those who are misguided.</p>
